title: Vlastimil Veselý
text: Vlastimil Veselý (born 6 May 1993 in <a href="Brno">Brno</a>) is a <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="FC%20Vyso%C4%8Dina%20Jihlava">FC Vysočina Jihlava</a> in <a href="Czech%20National%20Football%20League">Czech National Football League</a>.
